rescind_invite_v1(p_invite_id uuid):
- SECURITY DEFINER, search_path = public
- require_min_role_v1('admin') first executable statement
- Deletes pending invite row from public.tenant_invites
- Returns NOT_FOUND for accepted, expired, or cross-tenant invites
- Returns VALIDATION_ERROR if p_invite_id is null

